lead_paragraph: Kerwin Roach Jr. scored 15 points, all in the second half, and added six rebounds, as Texas closed the game on a 16-2 run to defeat Oklahoma State 62-50 Friday night in the regular season finale for both.

headline.print_headline: Big Second Half From Roach Leads Texas Past Oklahoma State
